{"tid":2215002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人搭親巴士都係咁？","createTime":"2020-09-23T16:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T16:25:19.000Z","uid":115142,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df847673b5eccdaad2aa71160c6287eade020908","tid":2215002,"uid":115142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T16:03:35.000Z","msg":"隔離嗰個人永遠都講緊電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成層得一個講緊電話一定係我隔離嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時仲要係菲律賓姐，佢地好興開晒facetime，要聽晒兩邊講嘢，仲要避唔好入鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日，隔離坐低咗個講緊電話既呀姐，都心知不秒，聽到佢話：「返去先講」，我開心咗一秒<br />\n點知，佢收咗線再打俾第二個，講到我落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要好大好大聲，好有情緒高低起伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講電話有時係避唔到我都明，但我放咗工塞返屋企已經好攰，可唔可以靜靜地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7b5d61356c29da565e35cd4ebee29cd0a19f81","tid":2215002,"uid":62648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"聽歌囉 我搭車一定聽歌的"},{"pid":"b0867998744bdbe919c5f23800126bd2245283ca","tid":2215002,"uid":115142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f7b5d61356c29da565e35cd4ebee29cd0a19f81","tid":2215002,"uid":62648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"聽歌囉 我搭車一定聽歌的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"都係既，但有時要開到好大聲先遮到，都係嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7791e64a9d6872922c36f7ee53266cf425b8777","tid":2215002,"uid":144537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu